title: PriPri Chii-chan!! (PriPri Chi-chan!!)
synopsis: The story revolves around a girl named Yuuka, who encounters a being from the depths of the Earth named Chii-chan (a pun of chiteijin, the Japanese word for underground-dweller), and an alien named Ucchan (a pun of uchuujin or alien). The story follows their heartwarming and chaotic everyday lives together.
voices: ['Murakawa, Rie', 'Nagae, Rika', 'Kurose, Yuuko', 'Asakura, Momo', 'Natsukawa, Shiina', 'Satou, Arise']
